snippet.title: Sven Co-op 4.0 Trailer 1
snippet.description:
Sven Co-op 4.0 for Half-Life ( http://www.svencoop.com ), Trailer 1.

Trailer by BMT & co. Music by Doc (remixed from Gluem's menu track). SC Team logo+animation by Karaduz.com.

Note that we've actually switched to a new Scientist model since this trailer was made, by the way :).
